<dl id="n42008a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42008a">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42008a"> 8(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Wolfe &amp; Montcalm</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">I went out, and walked two hours on the Plains of Abraham to breathe the pure and refreshing air of the mountain. There, alone, I sat on a stone, on the very spot where Wolfe and Montcalm had fought and died; <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 20</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: Opposing generals, British and French, at the siege of Quebec in 1758. </mm> </dd></dl>
